\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces After 16 iterations of value iteration, convergence is reached (when using $\gamma =0.99$ and $\eta =0.001$). For ealier stages of the algorithm see \autoref {fig:value_iteration_beginning} and \autoref {fig:value_iteration_halfway}. The agent will move to the right, end up in the top-right corner due to the stochastic wind, then work its way to the bottom-right and then to the left and up towards the goal.}}{2}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
